<collectingCountry id="E9CA7618FFF8FFD4FC12EE69FC09FB37" box="[932,993,1148,1169]" name="Egypt" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Egypt</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="F54C4B79FFF8FFD4FC59EE6EFF01FB08" author="ASSING V" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492" pagination="301 - 344" refId="ref22718" refString="ASSING V. (2008): A revision of the Micrillus species of the Palaearctic region, with notes on two species from adjacent parts of the Afrotropical and Oriental regions (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 1: 301 - 344." type="journal article" year="2008">ASSING 2008</bibRefCitation>
). The above specimens represent the first record from 
<collectingCountry id="E9CA7618FFF8FFD4FCAFEE8DFCB3FB08" box="[793,859,1176,1198]" name="Sudan" pageId="13" pageNumber="1492">Sudan</collectingCountry>
